One more important suggestion

Add these resource patterns into your configured excludePatterns too, if that is read from web.xml, so the exclusion is visible and maintainable:

<init-param>
    <param-name>excludePatterns</param-name>
    <param-value>
        /IPSWeb/services,
        /javax.faces.resource,
        /rfRes,
        /a4j
    </param-value>
</init-param>

That gives you both:
	•	config-level exclusion
	•	code-level safety net

